asiest part) and we were there 4 hours without getting the right spawn.  The other *easy* mob is Grimblox and this is what I read about him: <br>
 ~SolA - Hard part is getting there and clearing. Be prepared for a long camp. Mine was about 19 hours (57 spawns I think).~<br>
and then from another cleric:<br>
